original_title: Festival interceltique de Lorient - Le meilleur du grand spectacle 2020
overview: This real show brings together more than 500 artists from the Celtic planet around a fairyland of sounds and lights. Cyril Féraud takes us closer to the artists, on stage and behind the scenes of the show, in order to collect anecdotes and confidences from the musicians.
title: Festival interceltique de Lorient - Le meilleur du grand spectacle 2020
